WHAT IS DEVOPS - DevOps is a Methodology and it is a combinations of the terms "Development" and "Operation"
What is Automation - Automation basically combining of two words Automatic + Operation Automation is a creation of technology by which a process or procedure is accomplished without human assistance or minimal human assistance. 
What is Scaling - scaling is the property of the system to either expand or compress as needed.
What is infrastructure - infrastructure is the foundation or framework that supports a system or organization.
Why DevOps is Important - Actually in my point of view Devops is important because Continuous delivery of software
Better collaboration between teams
Easy deployment
Better efficiency and scalability
Errors are fixed at the initial stage
More security
Due to all these reasons DevOps is necessary
